        "X = np.arange(len(df_kospi))[:, np.newaxis]\n",

      "source": [
        "# LinearRegression"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 13,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "VpoQonB99kxj",
        "outputId": "09b8c199-a2b4-4676-ab25-df69c4540a51",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        }
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "execute_result",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "(array([-1.79633747]), 3300.0129403238802)"
            ]
          },
          "metadata": {},
          "execution_count": 13
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "from sklearn import linear_model\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "\n",
        "# 모델 준비\n",
        "model = linear_model.LinearRegression()\n",
        "\n",
        "# 데이터 준비 \n",
        "X = np.arange(len(df_kospi)).reshape(-1, 1)\n",
        "y = df_kospi['Close']\n",
        "\n",
        "# 훈련\n",
        "model.fit (X, y)\n",
        "\n",
        "model.coef_, model.intercept_"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 14,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "wkM2ZhCt9kxk",
        "outputId": "067d7cd1-d0a5-47ce-baea-f1539cb0fd87",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 265
        }
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "display_data",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "<Figure size 1008x288 with 1 Axes>"
            ],
            "image/png": "\n"
          },
          "metadata": {
            "needs_background": "light"
          }
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "x = np.arange(len(df_kospi))\n",
        "plt.plot(x, y)\n",
        "plt.plot(x, np.arange(len(df_kospi)) * model.coef_ + model.intercept_)\n",
        "plt.legend(['actual', 'prediction'])\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ]
    },

      "execution_count": 15,
